|_ JAVASCRIPT_|
.\___________/.

= JavaScript is implemented of all different browser, so there's no official download
  for the language. It's not like a python.
= ECMAscript is a reference that define the specification for the scripting language.
  = It describe how the language should work.
= The browser follow the ECMAscript rules and implemented them as JavaScript.
= This ECMAscript document we called:
  [0] ES2018
  [1] ES2017
  [2] ES2016
  [3] ES2015 (This is the beginning of ES6)
  
= If you need the documentation of javascript, you could go to this link:
  https://developer.mozilla.org
  